Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.14,0:24:05.28,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}よべるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:55.70,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一定是这样  当数不清的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:23:00.70,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}全部如愿之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:05.80,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我们还会贪婪地没有休止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.05,0:23:10.08,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}直到开始后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:12.73,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}永远过不够的昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.73,0:23:15.12,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}和不断积蓄的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:20.84,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就这样重叠着伴我前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.16,0:23:27.05,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}能够成为非常喜欢的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:32.12,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}非常喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:37.28,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}连这样的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.42,0:23:42.02,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我还无法完全相信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:46.72,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}总是难以如愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:52.44,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}多想再长高一些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.50,0:23:54.82,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愿我可以笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.89,0:23:57.30,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}用幸福
