Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.53,0:24:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,月火Da☆Yo！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:12.38,NoteV,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(1512,198)}月火DaYo！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.41,0:24:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,两个人合在一起就是Fire Sisters！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.38,0:24:14.51,Note,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(960,264)}我们是Fire Sisters！
